quoteText:
Customer information is a valuable business asset.
If for any reason We transfer or divest ourselves of our business assets, our customer information may be transferred as one of these business assets
title: The service can sell or otherwise transfer your personal data as part of a bankruptcy proceeding or other type of financial transaction.
